        <a href="/Content/Images/Docs/Screenshots/ConsultingTheSchedule.png" rel="lightbox" title="Fig 1: Consultando a agenda">
            <img src="/Content/Images/Docs/Screenshots/ConsultingTheSchedule-thumb.png" />
